	<Language_en_US>
		
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_SOMBRA_DEFEATED_1">
			<Text>Not Again!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_SOMBRA_DEFEATED_2">
			<Text>I AM NOT SO EASILY DEFEATED! MY VERY SHADOW SHALL CURSE YOUR LANDS!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_SOMBRA_EXPANSION_SERIOUS_WARNING_1">
			<Text>You encroach upon my land, MY VERY EMPIRE! LEAVE. NOW.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_SOMBRA_FIRSTGREETING_1">
			<Text>CRYSTAAAAAAAAAAAAALLSS.....Er, sorry, a thousand years of exile can change a pony. Now then, I am Sombra, King of the Crystal Empire. I do hope you came bearing gifts, maybe.....Crystals?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_SOMBRA_GREETING_HOSTILE_HELLO_1">
			<Text>Oh, hello. I was expecting a gift. I heard your kind make excellent laborers, especially in mines.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_SOMBRA_GREETING_NEUTRAL_HELLO_1">
			<Text>Oh flugelhorn, oh flugelhorn, oh how your sounds delight me. Oh..Er..Hello. My trumpeters were performing training excerises, yes. Training excerises. What can I do for you?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_SOMBRA_GREETING_POLITE_HELLO_1">
			<Text>Welcome! You're just in time to see me joust in the Crystal Festival, you surely have time to watch. Right?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_SOMBRA_HOSTILE_AGGRESSIVE_MILITARY_WARNING_1">
			<Text>Have you ever heard the sound of a flugelhorn? Amongst your troops? Perhaps my trumpeters should entertain your troops along my boarders. Remove them or I shall ponder the thought further.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_SOMBRA_OPEN_BORDERS_EXCHANGE_1">
			<Text>Our Empires are very much alike. We have castles, armies, crystals. Oh, you don't have crystals? Well allow my people to cross freely into your lands and crystals shall be had by all!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_SOMBRA_RESPONSE_REQUEST_1">
			<Text>It pains me greatly to ask this. I'm not use to this, asking. I'm doing it right, right?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_SOMBRA_LUXURY_TRADE_1">
			<Text>I'm not one to trade but I heard you might have some crystals. Care to trade for some flugelhorns? No? Then what?</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>



	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CIVILOPEDIA_LEADERS_SOMBRA_FACT_1">
			<Text>It is unknown what drove King Sombra down his path to darkness. Many statues of the king though can be seen with the name 'Somber' scratched out.</Text>
		</Row>
