		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CIVILOPEDIA_LEADERS_SOMBRA_SUBTITLE">
			<Text>King of the Crystal Empire</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CIVILOPEDIA_LEADERS_SOMBRA_TEXT_1">
			<Text>Sombra's origin remains shrounded in mystery, perhaps to his own liking. Where he came from, or who he was before he became the dark tyrant of the Crystal Empire remains unknown. His reign was terrible. He ruled his subjects with an iron hoof, using his crystal magic to terrorize and enslave them. His power could be felt all across Equestria, eventaully drawing hte attention of two sisters, Celestia and Luna. The two sisters defeated Sombra, banishing him to the arctic north, but not before he cursed his empire. The Crystal Empire vanished, along with its king. A thousand years later, after Nightmare Moon's return, the Crystal Empire reappeared. With its return, King Sombra has reawaken. With the return of Crystal Empire, King Sombra's influnce can once again be felt across Equestria. His actions are a mystery still. Will he return to his old ways? Or has a thousand years of exile changed the old king?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CIVILOPEDIA_LEADERS_SOMBRA_TITLES_1">
			<Text>King</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>

